<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Μενεσθιανὸς Ἀπολλωνιανῶι καὶ Σπαρ-

    <lb n="2"/>τιάτῃ  εὐθυμεῖν 

    <lb n="3"/>μάρτυρες οἱ θεοὶ <add place="supralinear">ὡς</add> πυθόμενος περὶ τοῦ κυρί-

    <lb n="4"/>ου μου, υ<hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>οῦ <choice><corr>ὑμῶν</corr><sic>ημων</sic></choice>, οὕτως ἠχθέσθην καὶ 

    <lb n="5"/>ἐπένθη<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear>α ὡς <hi rend="diaeresis">ἴ</hi>διον τέκνον· <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>ὶ γὰρ ἀξιο-

    <lb n="6"/>φίλητον <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ᾖν</unclear>· καὶ ὁρμὴν <subst><add place="inline">ἔχοντά</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ε<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">σ</del>χοντα</del></subst> με ἐξορμῆ-

    <lb n="7"/>σαι πρὸς ὑμᾶς Πινουτίων ἐπέσχεν, φάσ-

    <lb n="8"/>κων σὲ τὸν κύριόν μου Ἀπολλωνιανὸν 

    <lb n="9"/>παρηγγελκέναι αὐτῷ μὴ ἀνελθεῖν με 

    <lb n="10"/>ὡς σοῦ εἰς Ἀρσινοείτην γειν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>μένου. ἀλλὰ 

    <lb n="11"/>γενναίως φέρετε·  τοῦτο γὰρ καὶ τοῖς θεοῖς 

    <lb n="12"/>ἀπόκειται.  ἐν πᾶσί σοι, κύριέ μου Ἀπολλωνι-

    <lb n="13"/>ανέ, χάριτας ὁμολογῶ, ὅτι μου οὕτως προ<hi rend="diaeresis">ί</hi>-

    <lb n="14"/>στασαι ὡς σεαυτοῦ.  καὶ <choice><corr>ἐγὼ</corr><sic>καγω</sic></choice> δὲ νῦν δυνάμενος 

    <lb n="15"/>ἐμαυτὸν ἀμείψασθαι πρὸς τὸν Χαιρήμονα 

    <lb n="16"/>ἐφ᾽ οἷς με διέθετο, ἠνεσχόμην ἕως οὗ σοι δη-

    <lb n="17"/>λώσω.  οὐ γὰρ ἀνθρωπίνως ἔπραξεν, καὶ αὐ-

    <lb n="18"/>τὸς μὲν μετ᾽ ἄλλων πράγματα πράξας 

    <lb n="19"/>οὐδέπω οὐδὲν φάσκει τὰ ἐξ ἀν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">θρ</unclear>ώπων 

    <lb n="20"/>ἡμᾶς διαθέμενος. ὅ τι ο<add place="supralinear">ὖ</add><subst><add place="inline">ν</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">αν</del></subst> <add place="supralinear">ἐάν</add> σοι δοκῇ, δήλω-

    <lb n="21"/>σόν μοι· οὐ γὰρ ἡσυχάζω αὐτ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὸς</unclear>.  <hi rend="diaeresis">ἴ</hi>σον μέντοι τῆς 

    <lb n="22"/>χειρογραφίας ὑπὸ τοῦ διαπεμφθέντος γνω-

    <lb n="23"/>ρί<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μου</unclear> διεπεμψάμην σοι, <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να εἰδῇς.  καὶ <choice><corr>ἐγὼ</corr><sic>καγω</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="24"/>μὲν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Τ</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/>η <choice><corr>οἰκογενῆ</corr><sic>οικογενην</sic></choice> παῖδα ἀπ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ώλεσ</unclear>α 

    <lb n="25"/>ἄξιον ταλάντων δύο <num value="2"/>. <handShift new="m2"/> ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι, κύριέ 

    <lb n="26"/>μου, μετὰ κυρίου μου Σπαρτιάτου θεοῖς πᾶσιν 

    <lb n="27"/>εὐθυμοῦντα. 

    <lb n="28"/><handShift new="m1"/> ἐὰν ᾖ γενόμενα τὰ <choice><corr>προσαγ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">γ</supplied>έλματα</corr><sic>προσαγελματα</sic></choice>, πέμψον 

    <lb n="29"/><choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημειν</sic></choice>. 


    <lb n="30"/>τῆς δὲ <expan>χειρογρα<ex cert="high">φίας</ex></expan> ἐστὶν <expan>ἀντίγρα<ex cert="high">φον</ex></expan>· 
<milestone rend="paragraphos" unit="undefined"/>
    <lb n="31"/><expan>Αὐρ<ex cert="high">ηλίῳ</ex></expan> Παυλείνῳ <expan>στρα<ex cert="high">τηγῷ</ex></expan> <expan>Ἑρμοπολ<ex cert="high">ίτου</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="31"/>παρὰ Μάρκου <expan>Αὐρ<ex cert="high">ηλίου</ex></expan> Διονυσίου καὶ <expan>Αὐρ<ex cert="high">ηλίου</ex></expan> Ἀμμωνίου 

    <lb n="32"/>ἀπὸ <expan>Ὀξ<ex cert="high">υρύγχων</ex></expan> <expan>πόλ<ex cert="high">εως</ex></expan>. συναπεστάλημεν ὑπὸ <expan>Αὐρ<ex cert="high">ηλίου</ex></expan> Λεωνίδου 

    <lb n="33"/><expan>στρα<ex cert="high">τηγοῦ</ex></expan> <expan>Ὀξυρυγχ<ex cert="high">ίτου</ex></expan>, ἐκ τῶν γραφέντων αὐτῷ ὑπὸ <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>ου-

    <lb n="34"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λ</unclear>ίου <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>ουλιανοῦ τοῦ <expan>κρα<ex cert="high">τίστου</ex></expan> <expan>ἐπιστρα<ex cert="high">τήγου</ex></expan>, πρὸς ἃ ἀνήνεγκας 

    <lb n="35"/>αὐτῷ, γενέσθαι ἐνταῦθα καὶ γνωρίσαι <choice><corr>τοὺ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ς</supplied></corr><sic>του</sic></choice> δηλωθέν-

    <lb n="36"/>τας ὑπὸ Τίτου <expan>Φλ<ex cert="high">αυίου</ex></expan> Χαιρήμονος ἀμφοδογραμμα-

    <lb n="37"/>τέως τῆς <expan>Ὀξ<ex cert="high">υρύγχων</ex></expan> <expan>πόλ<ex cert="high">εως</ex></expan> ἄνδρας ἀριθμῷ <num value="5">ε</num>.  ὀμνύομεν τὴν 

    <lb n="38"/>Γα<hi rend="diaeresis">ί</hi>ου <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>ουλίου Οὐήρου <choice><corr>Μαξιμίνου</corr><sic>μαξιμεινου</sic></choice> Καίσαρος τοῦ κυρίου 

    <lb n="39"/>τύχην <choice><corr>ἐπιδεδημηκότες</corr><sic>επιδεδημηκοτα</sic></choice> τοῖς ἐνθάδε μεμαθηκέναι 

    <lb n="40"/>τούτους εἰς τὴν ἰδίαν ἀποδεδημηκέναι ἀντιλημ-

    <lb n="41"/>ψομένους τῶν ἐπιβαλλ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ουσ</unclear>ῶν αὐτοῖς χρειῶν· 

    <lb n="42"/>ἢ ἔνοχοι εἴημεν τῷ ὅρκῳ.  <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="2">β</num>, Χοίακ <num value="17">ιζ</num> 

    <lb n="43"/><expan>τι<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> καὶ <expan>τι<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> δι᾽ ἐμοῦ <expan>τι<ex cert="high">νὸς</ex></expan> ὠμόσαμεν τὸν <expan>ὅρκο<ex cert="high">ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="44"/>ὡς πρόκειτ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αι</unclear>. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="47"/>Αὐρηλίωι Ἀπολλωνιανῶι <gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><abbr><gap reason="lost" extent="4" unit="character"/>γυμνασιαρχ</abbr> <expan>στρα<ex cert="high">τηγήσαντι</ex></expan> νομῶν. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.17411" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.17411" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="0235-12-14">nach 14. Dez. 235</date></p></div><div n="meta.17411" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 44: <date type="mentioned" value="0235-12-14">14. Dez. 235</date></p></div><div n="meta.17411" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">PSI</title><biblScope type="volume">12</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1248</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">17411</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0238</series>; <biblScope type="volume">12</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1248</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0238;12;1248" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.17411" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">321</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">250</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.17411" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="com